description.en: ICHI is a Decentralized Autonomous Organization (DAO) that gives crypto projects the tools they need to participate in DeFi more efficiently. ICHI creates products that allow a project to develop its own stable asset (backed by its community’s token), and its own liquidity programs that turn Total Value Locked into Protocol Owned Liquidity.
